  </developer>
  <summary>Post-production for screen recordings</summary>
  <description>
    <p>
      Unisic Studio is a post-production tool for screen recordings on Linux
      Wayland. It turns a raw capture into a polished video: automatic zoom and
      pan driven by cursor and click tracks, styling, and export via ffmpeg.
      It is a sibling of Unisic and shares its foundation library.
    </p>
  </description>
